UCL & Intel® VisualNav v2 - Facial Navigation for Visual Studio using OpenVino Technology

A downloadable extension to provide accessibility in navigating developer components in Visual Studio

Project Vision

Existing tools do not provide enough support for those with disability. Our application, VisualNav is a first-of-its-kind touchless environment for coding, offering a new visual paradigm to traditional development.

Our vision is for developers with a disability to be able to work together in a live share environment at the same productivity level as their peers.
